# Astro build-time public vars. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) only if you want a
# local production build/preview to embed the real Turnstile widget.
#
# NOTE: `just wrangler-dev` and local endpoint testing intentionally rely on the
# built-in Cloudflare Turnstile *test* key (the page falls back to it when this
# is unset), which always passes on localhost. Setting the real key below makes
# the widget expect the production domain, so leave `.env` absent for local dev.
#
# The production deploy injects this automatically (see .github/workflows/ci.yml).
# This value is a PUBLIC site key (rendered into the page HTML) — not a secret.
# Its secret counterpart is the TURNSTILE_SECRET Worker secret (wrangler secret put).
PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=0x4AAAAAAD7jYecPL3c82-lW
